Object.Field: SELECT a.I_PACKAGE OBJECT_ID, 'SnpPackage' OBJECT_CLASS, 'PACK_' || a.PACK_NAME || '.xml' FILE_NAME FROM <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("D")%>.SNP_PACKAGE a INNER JOIN <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("D")%>.SNP_FOLDER b ON a.I_FOLDER = b.I_FOLDER INNER JOIN <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("D")%>.SNP_PROJECT c ON b.I_PROJECT = c.I_PROJECT WHERE c.I_PROJECT = '<%= odiRef.getOption("PROJECT_ID") %>'
